      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Andrew Tridgell</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Andrew_Tridgell.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Andrew_Tridgell.jpg/330px-Andrew_Tridgell.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"400\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Andrew_Tridgell.jpg/500px-Andrew_Tridgell.jpg 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Andrew_Tridgell.jpg/960px-Andrew_Tridgell.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Andrew_Tridgell.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Andrew Tridgell <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Andrew Tridgell</b>,<br />\nan Australian programmer, primary author of the <a href=\"/Temporal_Difference_Learning\" title=\"Temporal Difference Learning\">TD-learning</a> chess program <a href=\"/KnightCap\" title=\"KnightCap\">KnightCap</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> and best known as the major developer of the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Samba_%28software%29\">Samba</a> software. His Ph.D. thesis <i>Efficient Algorithms for Sorting and Synchronization</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> at the <a href=\"/Australian_National_University\" title=\"Australian National University\">Australian National University</a> was based on his work on the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rsync\">rsync</a> algorithm.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1995_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1995 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andrew_Tridgell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1995_...\">1995 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andrew_Tridgell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 1995 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrew Tridgell</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#Brent\" title=\"Mathematician\">Richard P. Brent</a> (<b>1995</b>). <i>A General-Purpose Parallel Sorting Algorithm</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/journals/ijhsc/ijhsc7.html\">International Journal of High Speed Computing, Vol. 7</a>, No. 2, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://maths-people.anu.edu.au/~brent/pd/rpb158.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrew Tridgell</a> (<b>1995</b>). <i>Landslide Victory for Computers</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#18_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICCA Journal, Vol. 18,  No. 3</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/ANU_Carbon-Silicon_Tournaments#1995\" title=\"ANU Carbon-Silicon Tournaments\">ANU Carbon-Silicon Tournament 1995</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrew Tridgell</a> (<b>1997</b>). <i>KnightCap — a parallel chess program on the AP1000+</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ftp.riken.jp/pub/net/samba/tridge/knightcap_pcw97.ps.gz\">zipped ps</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jonathan_Baxter\" title=\"Jonathan Baxter\">Jonathan Baxter</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrew Tridgell</a>, <a href=\"/Lex_Weaver\" title=\"Lex Weaver\">Lex Weaver</a> (<b>1997</b>). <i>Knightcap: A chess program that learns by combining td(λ) with minimax search</i>. 15th International Conference on Machine Learning, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://citeseerx.ist.psu.edu/viewdoc/download?doi=10.1.1.54.8263&amp;rep=rep1&amp;type=pdf\">pdf</a> via <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://citeseerx.ist.psu.edu/viewdoc/summary?doi=10.1.1.54.8263\">citeseerX</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jonathan_Baxter\" title=\"Jonathan Baxter\">Jonathan Baxter</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrew Tridgell</a>, <a href=\"/Lex_Weaver\" title=\"Lex Weaver\">Lex Weaver</a> (<b>1998</b>). <i>Experiments in Parameter Learning Using Temporal Differences</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#21_2\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICCA Journal, Vol. 21,  No. 2</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jonathan_Baxter\" title=\"Jonathan Baxter\">Jonathan Baxter</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrew Tridgell</a>, <a href=\"/Lex_Weaver\" title=\"Lex Weaver\">Lex Weaver</a> (<b>1999</b>). <i>TDLeaf(lambda): Combining Temporal Difference Learning with Game-Tree Search</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.chatbots.org/journal/australian_journal_of_intelligent_information_processing_systems/\">Australian Journal of Intelligent Information Processing Systems</a>, Vol. 5 No. 1, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://arxiv.org/abs/cs/9901001\">arXiv:cs/9901001</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jonathan_Baxter\" title=\"Jonathan Baxter\">Jonathan Baxter</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrew Tridgell</a>, <a href=\"/Lex_Weaver\" title=\"Lex Weaver\">Lex Weaver</a> (<b>1999</b>). <i>KnightCap: A chess program that learns by combining TD(lambda) with game-tree search</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/cs/9901002\">arXiv:cs/9901002</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrew Tridgell</a> (<b>1999</b>). <i>Efficient Algorithms for Sorting and Synchronization</i>. Ph.D. thesis, <a href=\"/Australian_National_University\" title=\"Australian National University\">Australian National University</a>, advisor <a href=\"/Mathematician#Brent\" title=\"Mathematician\">Richard P. Brent</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://samba.org/~tridge/phd_thesis.pdf\">pdf</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andrew_Tridgell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Jonathan_Baxter\" title=\"Jonathan Baxter\">Jonathan Baxter</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrew Tridgell</a>, <a href=\"/Lex_Weaver\" title=\"Lex Weaver\">Lex Weaver</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i>Learning to Play Chess Using Temporal Differences</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.dblp.org/db/journals/ml/ml40.html#BaxterTW00\">Machine Learning, Vol 40, No. 3</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.princeton.edu/courses/archive/fall06/cos402/papers/chess-RL.pdf\">pdf</a> </li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andrew_Tridgell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/group/rec.games.chess.computer/browse_frm/thread/1f7ba9d3c31f071\">KnightCap 1.0</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrew Tridgell</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, February 27, 1997 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/group/rec.games.chess.computer/msg/ded7e4e4304d8d4e\">Re: Going commercial, maybe</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrew Tridgell</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, March 9, 1997&#160;» <a href=\"/3D_Graphics_Board\" title=\"3D Graphics Board\">3D Graphics Board</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/group/rec.games.chess.computer/msg/708196e40e9a4a7f\">Re: Computer Chess Planning</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrew Tridgell</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, March 17, 1997 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/group/rec.games.chess.computer/browse_frm/thread/5a5ec0faffa05984\">Parallel searching</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrew Tridgell</a>, post 16, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, March 22, 1997&#160;» <a href=\"/Parallel_Search\" title=\"Parallel Search\">Parallel Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/group/rec.games.chess.computer/browse_frm/thread/e68ee1ab5a2603d3\">KnightCap v1.8</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrew Tridgell</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, April 03, 1997</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/group/rec.games.chess.computer/msg/300171a5fa7ce7b6\">Re: computer chess \"oracle\" ideas...</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrew Tridgell</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, April 03, 1997&#160;» <a href=\"/Oracle\" title=\"Oracle\">Oracle</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/group/rec.games.chess.computer/browse_frm/thread/ca0300b50438a388\">quiescence search</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrew Tridgell</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, April 16, 1997&#160;» <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a>, <a href=\"/Check\" title=\"Check\">Check</a>, <a href=\"/Crafty\" title=\"Crafty\">Crafty</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/group/rec.games.chess.computer/msg/4d6c328e8e8e0cd4\">Re: Bit Board Bonkers?? - other alternatives</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrew Tridgell</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, August 9, 1997&#160;» <a href=\"/Piece-Sets\" title=\"Piece-Sets\">Piece-Sets</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/group/rec.games.chess.computer/msg/f9bfe5d4457a19ad\">asymmetry</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrew Tridgell</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, August 12, 1997&#160;» <a href=\"/Asymmetric_Evaluation\" title=\"Asymmetric Evaluation\">Asymmetric Evaluation</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andrew_Tridgell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.samba.org/%7Etridge/\">Andrew Tridgell's homepage</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Andrew_Tridgell\">Andrew Tridgell from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://genealogy.math.ndsu.nodak.edu/id.php?id=59310\">The Mathematics Genealogy Project - Andrew Tridgell</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://chessexpress.blogspot.de/2007/07/tridge.html\">chessexpress: Tridge</a> by <a href=\"/Shaun_Press\" title=\"Shaun Press\">Shaun Press</a>, July 23, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://diydrones.com/profile/AndrewTridgell\">Andrew Tridgell's Page - DIY Drones</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andrew_Tridgell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Photo by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.flickr.com/people/46888841@N00\">Gopal Vijayaraghavan</a>,  January 28, 2006, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Category:Andrew_Tridgell\">Category:Andrew Tridgell - Wikimedia Commons</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://samba.org/KnightCap/\">Welcome to the KnightCap home page</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrew Tridgell</a> (<b>1999</b>). <i>Efficient Algorithms for Sorting and Synchronization</i>. Ph.D. thesis, The <a href=\"/Australian_National_University\" title=\"Australian National University\">Australian National University</a>, advisor <a href=\"/Mathematician#Brent\" title=\"Mathematician\">Richard P. Brent</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://samba.org/~tridge/phd_thesis.pdf\">pdf</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://dblp.org/pers/hd/t/Tridgell:Andrew.html\">dblp: Andrew Tridgell</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301023804\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.066 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.600 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 83/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 174/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:3359-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301023804 a